Adrianna has lost only one regular season match in her career. That loss was to Wenona and only by 63pts. Currently ranked 5th after one win this season, Adrianna is looking for sweet brutal revenge on her one and only season loss.
Last year Wenona finished ranked 5th over all! This will be her first season 6 match up as she was part of the Tag Team league this year. Wenona wants her number 5 ranking back. She beat Adrianna once, she can do it again!
This match has it all: back and forth scoring, brutal submissions from crushing leg scissors, and the loser getting bound up like a pretzel and fucked like the loser she is!
Do not miss this amazing, painful, hard-fought match!
title: Wenona "The Gymnast" (0-0)
